</code></pre></div></div>

<ol>
  <li>Â (BE CAREFUL YOU GET THE DISK NUMBER RIGHT IN THIS STEP) Assuming the ubuntu iso file is XX.iso, write to usb using</li>
</ol>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;code&gt;sudo dd if=XX.iso of=/dev/rdisk2 bs=4m&lt;/code&gt;
